				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${L}_{d}^{fractal}$$\end{document}Ldfractal slightly decreases with increasing cascade density.

