				\begin{document}$$\sim 5$$\end{document}∼5%). In each irradiation run, the total ion dose (Φ) was split into a train of equal square pulses. This was done by using a pulse generator with rise and fall times of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
